        <h3 class="section-heading">ABOUT US</h3>
        <div class="sec-content-div flexible">
          <p>
            Bean cafe is a coffee shop that provides you with quality coffee that helps boost your productivity and helps build your mood. From the farmers who tend to the red-ripe coffee cherries, to the master roasters who coax the best from every bean, and to the barista who serves it with care. We are committed to the highest standards of quality and service, embracing our heritage while innovating to create new experiences to savor. 
Having  cup of coffee is good, but having a cup of real coffee is greater. There is no doubt that you will enjoy this coffee more than other you have ever tasted.
          </p>
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520284888530-ac9a909a1b62?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80" alt="Man preparing a freshly brewed coffee" />
