      <section id="varieties" class="sec-padding">
        <h3 class="section-heading">VARIETIES</h3>
        <div class="sec-content-div flexible">
          <div class="tile">
            <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1303583671/photo/cup-glass-of-coffee-with-smoke-and-coffee-beans-on-old-wooden-background.webp?b=1&s=170667a&w=0&k=20&c=aVldamhbluP7K6ACdAEir6X8mGH7zwPur0p0mZWSXYI=" alt="Espresso" />
            <h4>Espresso</h4>
            <p>
              Espresso is the embodiment of concentration and intensity. Brewed to perfection, it exudes a rich, dark elixir, crowned with a velvety crema. Sip this Italian masterpiece for an instant journey to the heart of coffee's allure.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1462917882517-e150004895fa?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1yZWxhdGVkfDEyfHx8ZW58MHx8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=60"
              alt="Capuccino"
            />
            <h4>Capuccino</h4>
            <p>
              A masterpiece of balance, the cappuccino is a harmonious trio of espresso, steamed milk, and airy foam. With a tantalizing swirl of artful foam on its surface, it promises a perfect blend of strength and silkiness, satisfying the most refined palate.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <img src="https://enjoyjava.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/how-to-make-an-americano.jpg"
 alt="Americano" />
            <h4>Americano</h4>
            <p>
             The Americano is the embodiment of liberation in simplicity. A bold espresso liberated by hot water, it offers an uncomplicated and dignified caffeine experience that is as pure as it is profound.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461023058943-07fcbe16d735?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2069&q=80" alt="Latte" />
            <h4>Latte</h4>
            <p>
              Elegance in a glass, the latte is a canvas for coffee artistry. Smooth and inviting, it marries espresso's vigor with a lavish canvas of steamed milk, creating a canvas for coffee artistry. Each sip is a journey through a cloud of coffee heaven.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <img src="https://wetheorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Mocha-Coffee-image-2-scaled.jpg" alt="Mocha" />
            <h4>Mocha</h4>
            <p>
              A divine fusion of two worlds, the mocha is an opulent indulgence. The marriage of espresso's intensity with the seduction of chocolate creates a lush and velvety elixir that beckons to the connoisseur and the romantic alike.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="tile">
            <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/681493700/photo/frappuccino-in-takeaway-cup.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=lA2Fj-ILerew4wgDvqsNmte5oCHXKssP9J-vdWs-J8s=" alt="Frappuccino" />
            <h4>Frappuccino</h4>
            <p>
              This icy concoction starts with a base of freshly brewed coffee or coffee-flavored syrup, combined with milk, ice, and a touch of sweetness. It is then expertly blended to perfection, resulting in a creamy, frosty masterpiece. 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
